longBusinessSummary: Thunderful Group AB invests, develops, and publishes digital games primarily for PC and console platforms in Sweden. It operates through two segments: Publishing and Co-Development and Services. It also develops game on behalf of external license and IP owners; and provides consultative publishing support services. Thunderful Group AB was founded in 1965 and is headquartered in Gothenburg, Sweden.
